name: Whole World Woman
description: "As a woman I have no country. As a woman I want no country. As a woman, my country is the whole world." Virginia Woolf In this designe I expressed the quote above by using a woman above the cloud "which gives the viewer feeling that she is above the whole world " and she took something impossible with her "and it is the whale above the clouds " this whale means that she is in control she has the whole world .
